NAME		cube.row
SYNTAX		cube.row <panel> <layer> [red green blue]
DESCRIPTION	Set all LEDs in a row to the same colour. If the optional
		red, green and blue arguments are provided then that colour
		is used, otherwise the current working colour is used.
RETURN VALUE	None
EXAMPLES	Fill the row on panel 2, layer 3 with the current colour:
			cube.row 2 3
		Fill the row on panel 2, layer 3 with blue:
			cube.row 2 3 0 0 63
SEE ALSO	cube.colour, cube.column
